name: Young-Geun Choi
body:
My research interests broadly lie on unsupervised learning from data and public health
studies. My thesis deals with structured covariance matrix estimation and its application
in large-scale data. I also have involved in research on random matrix theory, longitudinal
cohort study, electronic medical record, and analysis of mass-spectrometry data.
